originalText.text: Lisa is absolutely amazing! We got so many compliments on how great our ceremony was. Lisa is so warm and made us feel so comfortable from the start. She really took the time to get to know my husband and I, and made the ceremony personalized to us. It was a perfect mix of sappy, sweet, and funny and it flowed so well. Many people told us that it was the best ceremony they have ever been to. We are so grateful for Lisa for making our special day even that much more special.

originalText.text: Echoing the sentiments of the previous reviews, hiring Lisa was one of the best decisions my husband and I made for our wedding day. Lisa made our ceremony incredibly special - it far exceeded our expectations! She took the time to get to know us which resulted in a perfectly curated and personal ceremony. We received so many compliments and our guests kept asking if Lisa was a family member or dear family friend. Her professionalism, warmth and expertise is unmatched. We cannot recommend her enough!!

originalText.text: Working with Lisa was the best decision we made - she did a phenomenal job curating our ceremony and we could not have been happier!! It was absolutely perfect, and completely "us". Not to mention she is incredibly eloquent, elegant, and chic. Our ceremony was one we will always remember, and we still get so many compliments on it to this day! It most definitely left an impression on not only us, but our guests. We love Lisa!
